PN,36601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,7,Fdeath was contributed to by a brain
OL,8,Fcondition caused by repeatedly heading
OL,9,Fa football, a coroner has ruled.
OL,11,FStiles, a Manchester United legend and
OL,12,F1966 World Cup winner, died with
OL,13,Fsevere dementia and had headed a
OL,14,Ffootball around 140,000 times during
OL,15,Fhis career, Stockport Coroner's Court
OL,16,Fheard at the inquest into his death.
OL,18,FHe donated his brain to medical
OL,19,Fresearch into the potential link
OL,20,Fbetween heading and brain injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FExpert analysis of his brain showed
OL,7,Fhis severe dementia was as a result of
OL,8,FAlzheimer's disease but also the
OL,9,Fcondition, chronic traumatic
OL,10,Fencephalopathy (CTE), which is
OL,11,Fassociated with head trauma from
OL,12,Fheading a ball.
OL,14,FNeuro-pathology expert, Dr Daniel Du
OL,15,FPlessis told the court: "I'm quite
OL,16,Fconvinced his heading the football
OL,17,Fthat many times has caused his CTE."
OL,26,@wD@YOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FAlison Mutch, senior coroner for South
OL,7,FManchester, asked Dr Du Plessis: "You
OL,8,Fare saying repeated heading of the
OL,9,Fball is the cause of his CTE?"
OL,11,F"Yes," Dr Du Plessis replied.
OL,13,FNorbert "Nobby" Stiles, born in
OL,14,FManchester in 1942, was a tough-
OL,15,Ftackling defensive midfielder, capped
OL,16,F28 times by England and played nearly
OL,17,F400 times for Manchester United.
OL,26,@oD@bOUqD@^O]sD@AOUsD@FO]uD@IOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FHe died in October 2020 at the age of
OL,7,F78 after a long illness but his family
OL,8,Fhas since campaigned for football
OL,9,Fauthorities to do more to help ex-
OL,10,Fplayers cope with injuries they claim
OL,11,Fwere caused during their playing days.
OL,13,FStiles's son John has previously said
OL,14,Fthat football had "killed" his father.
OL,16,FMr Stiles told the hearing: "My dad
OL,17,Fwas very humble, he just happened to
OL,18,Fhave achieved quite a lot. It never
OL,19,Freally changed him.
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@ZO]xD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,F"If you went into his house you would
OL,7,Fnever know he was a footballer. He was
OL,8,Fvery much a family man, football was
OL,9,Fleft at the door. The family was
OL,10,Falways the first priority."
OL,12,FJohn is head of the Football Families
OL,13,Ffor Justice (FFJ) group which is
OL,14,Fcalling on the football authorities to
OL,15,Fdo more after his father was forced to
OL,16,Fsell his winner's medals to fund his
OL,17,Fdementia care.
OL,26,@rD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FHe is among dozens of former
OL,7,Ffootballers and their families suing
OL,8,Fthe Football Association, the Football
OL,9,FAssociation of Wales and the English
OL,10,FFootball League over claims they were
OL,11,F"negligent and in breach of their duty
OL,12,Fof care" to the former players.
OL,14,FLawyers for the former players and
OL,15,Ftheir families have previously said
OL,16,Ffootball bodies knew or should have
OL,17,Fknown that repeatedly heading a ball
OL,18,Fin training and during matches was
OL,19,Flikely to cause brain injuries, and
OL,20,Fthat the risks were known for decades.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FIn March this year lawyers for The
OL,7,FFootball Association (FA) told the
OL,8,FHigh Court it has "not been
OL,9,Festablished by science" that heading a
OL,10,Fball or "occasional" concussion can
OL,11,Flead to permanent brain damage.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the inquest ruling at
OL,14,FStockport Coroners' Court on
OL,15,FWednesday, 15 July, John Stiles said
OL,16,Fhe "we don't need anymore research" to
OL,17,Fprove the links between brain injuries
OL,18,Fand heading the ball.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@WO]rD@IOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FHe said: "We need to help families
OL,7,Fwhere their loved ones are going into
OL,8,Fcare homes."
OL,10,FA spokesperson from the FA said:
OL,11,F"While the link between heading in
OL,12,Ffootball and long-term brain health
OL,13,Fremains the subject of ongoing
OL,14,Fscientific and medical research, we
OL,15,Fhave consistently been at the
OL,16,Fforefront of efforts to help improve
OL,17,Fthe safety of our game.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,F"We have led the way in this area to
OL,7,Fproactively review and strengthen
OL,8,Fplayer welfare across every level of
OL,9,FEnglish football, working closely with
OL,10,Four domestic and international
OL,11,Fstakeholders.
OL,13,F"We were the first governing body to
OL,14,Fintroduce comprehensive heading
OL,15,Fguidelines across both professional
OL,16,Fand grassroots football, and we
OL,17,Fcontinue to review and enhance our
OL,18,Fgame-wide concussion protocols in line
OL,19,Fwith worldwide best practice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,F"We have also invested in and actively
OL,7,Fsupported multiple independent
OL,8,Fresearch projects, often resulting in
OL,9,Fgroundbreaking and valuable insight,
OL,10,Fin order to gain a greater
OL,11,Funderstanding of this complex area
OL,12,Fthrough objective, robust and thorough
OL,13,Fanalysis."
OL,15,FIn January an inquest into the death
OL,16,Fof ex-Scotland, Manchester United and
OL,17,FLeeds defender Gordon McQueen, at the
OL,18,Fage of 70, found that heading the ball
OL,19,Fwas "likely" to have contributed to a
OL,20,Fbrain injury which was a factor in his
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,26,@{D@EOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FMcQueen was also diagnosed with CTE.
OL,8,FMcQueen's TV presenter daughter Hayley
OL,9,FMcQueen said England's 1966 World Cup-
OL,10,Fwinning team had now been "pretty much
OL,11,Fwiped out" by neurodegenerative
OL,12,Fdisease.
OL,14,FThe FA co-funded, with the
OL,15,FProfessional Footballers' Association,
OL,16,Fa 2019 study that found footballers
OL,17,Fwere three and a half times more
OL,18,Flikely to die of neurodegenerative
OL,19,Fdisease than age-matched members of
OL,20,Fthe general population.
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles'
OL,4,Cdeath linked to heading footballs
OL,6,FThe FA is phasing out all heading in
OL,7,Fyouth football up to under-11s by 2026.
OL,9,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,10,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,11,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,12,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,13,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,14,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
